div.div: This activity diagram shows the execution of the backup jobs. First of all, you choose whether you want to run all the jobs or not. If yes, it executes all the jobs (full or differential) then writes the corresponding logs and sends a notification to the user. If not, it performs the same actions but only for a backup job we have chosen.
